{
  "stem": "8072.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just alone, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we got there, and-- which was in March, and at that time, you know, I-- I-- when-- when I saw what's going on, I-- I always thought in my mind I knew that the war has to be-- probably would be over in about another five, six weeks.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's-- was close to Passover, that by Passover the war's going to be over.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And since-- if my sisters, my brother, if they find out I was sent to Auschwitz, so they probably later on know for sure that I'm not going to be alive.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm gonna surprise everybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm gonna fight, and I'm gonna make it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm gonna be alive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, I don't care if I don't eat for six weeks or if I don't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm going to somehow manage to stay alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when they-- when they gave you the-- they give you food, like rations.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was like called a soup.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They brought it in a barrel, and they give it to you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Basically a lot of times, if they had some left over, they give some to the younger.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When I was there, I think I was the youngest one in the group at that time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they would give me another portion.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then another thing what I did is when they emptied the food, when they emptied the barrels, they had to take them back to the-- like the mess hall, which was, I don't know, four, five barracks or something like that.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I always jumped out, and I'm going to carry the barrels back to the thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So when you--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the mess hall.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
